data.description: Amazing custom built craftsman perfect for multi-generational living.  Entertain or relax in the custom designed back yard complete with a resort-like pool and spa, private basketball court, and in-ground trampoline. Interior features include Master on main, 2 story great room, executive library, keeping room, upgraded trim and hardwood floors.  Terrace level is fully finished with kitchen and can be accessed from the front and back yard.
